{"tid":1843281,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"粉嶺暉明樓 隔離就係和合石，極懷疑主要係住病人，死咗就即火化","createTime":"2020-01-26T06:40:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T08:33:03.000Z","uid":48083,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1733349220c3132fe15e5f90e511521a29d658ca","tid":1843281,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:40:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SCbTv2J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSCbTv2J.png&h=3ccd307a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知後山有冇秘道直去<br />\nGoogle map 只需10分鐘（經過哂民居）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QgLXXNF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQgLXXNF.png&h=45d25978&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然離北區醫院都係十分鐘車程<br />\n但冇撚理由醫護人員收工仲同懷疑病患住咁近啩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以極懷疑主要係住病人<br />\n仲要係重病就死既<br />\n<br />\n查實最合理，係徵用哥爾夫球場起臨時屋<br />\n做隔離病房<br />\n暉明樓只係俾醫護人員住<br />\n<br />\nGolf 場係正北區醫院隔離<br />\n大撚到爆<br />\n可以做到懷疑病人之間有較安全間隔<br />\n<br />\n而且附近冇民居<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Eoc0a3c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEoc0a3c.png&h=c4e1ebd4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"087ebd8a6dc1c7ad5a4fd9e03cc4f9cd5717418b","tid":1843281,"uid":169074,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:41:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1fb868a7d71f814a89de379c86cedc2986734696","tid":1843281,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:46:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9347f0d524f203c6b32822e034be0d520eb5b836","tid":1843281,"uid":280886,"like":0,"dis